{
  "stem": "12022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's what I did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I go-- was going behind the German army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, when I saw where is the village, close, what I go in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I go in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I speak perfect Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they couldn't recognize me as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They gave me food and shelter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the next day, I am taking off again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was going every day behind the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I came to one little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I know the Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He don't know me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I don't know him either, just-- they told me where he lives down there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When I met him, he took me in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he locked me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was sitting by myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I was so lonely, to nobody to-- and I don't know anything what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was watching through the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "A little boy come out, a Lithuanian, and start to dance a Russian dance and sing Russian, maybe [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The way was [INAUDIBLE] my heart, I laugh, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And his mother come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And she start to take him-- she chase him away, take him-- took him home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "After I left from down there, I was going, again, farther.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After I was going down there farther.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And down there was a big airport the Russians was build-- building, a huge air-- a military airport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When the Germans invaded, they took it over, the airport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And when I was close to the airport, Russian planes come over to bomb the airport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the Germans fleet, the, the fighters, they-- right away, they took, took off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "The fighters, the fighters shot down, right away, the three Russian planes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, here I am down there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
